Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:19.23,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:25.05,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沒有星光的迷宮裡掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.90,0:00:30.08,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨的少年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.65,0:00:35.80,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受靈魂的吶喊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:41.05,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宇宙正在呼喚你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:46.85,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背負傷痕 知曉孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.35,0:00:52.20,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於明白了羈絆的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.35,0:00:55.06,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消除陰翳眼眸中的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.30,0:00:57.69,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不安和困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:04.20,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.57,0:01:08.03,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士們 站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:10.70,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.90,0:01:14.12,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果背負的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.25,0:01:16.05,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠稱為愛的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.13,0:01:18.75,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士們相互支持
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.90,0:01:21.38,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化為風的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.67,0:01:25.85,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全新的Ω神話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.97,0:01:31.10,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就從現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:20.70,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光榮字幕組&galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:02:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 沒事嗎 小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.57,0:02:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是小馬座藏匿的那群人之一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 終於找到了 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能告訴我們 你們藏在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬座？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在看哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.25,0:02:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你們背後可是門戶大開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:02:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼天馬座他們會在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.78,0:03:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.71,0:03:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪那個叫什麼米拉的 害我根本不在狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勒利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止克勒利斯一派 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要同時應付天馬座他們 太棘手了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.82,0:04:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勒利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:45.25,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞勒涅（Selene），名字來源於希臘神話月亮女神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞勒涅 沒受傷吧   
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是聖鬥士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被詛咒的聖衣！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小馬座的聖鬥士！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜尋未失去時間的人類的士兵報告說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們湊巧發現了天馬座等人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說正在逼近這座城
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您放心 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬座等人會由我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.78,0:05:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忒拜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這任務 請務必交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.02,0:05:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次 我一定會擊敗那群軟弱的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群傢伙是我的獵物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忒拜 不許你橫插一槍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那是我的獵物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 不准他們再向前一步 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你二人給我好好迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我是想幫克勒利斯包紮一下傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.81,0:05:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你這份溫柔的心意已經足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:06:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這份心意足以治癒我的傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以塞勒涅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做危險的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.65,0:06:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬座
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到 竟能見到天馬座
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 請問您是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.17,0:06:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是克勒利斯 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:38.50,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勒利斯（Celeris），希臘神話中的名馬，小馬座出典的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Equuleus小馬座的克勒利斯    
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Equuleus小馬座…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.01,0:06:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小馬座是閃耀在天馬座旁邊 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也被稱作是天馬座的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教啊 兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說是兄弟不如說是… 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勒利斯 快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 馬上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 有話一會兒再說 上車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.01,0:07:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 抱歉我們在趕路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.86,0:07:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要去帕拉斯的城堡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就更該上車了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是塞勒涅 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榮斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫龍峰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是昴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.73,0:07:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的名字都好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前在童話裡聽過這個詞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然一個人孤軍奮戰…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在前面的隧道下車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 那些人不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 為了保證安全 他們會走其他的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前是有滑輪車的 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以走其他的樓梯 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這邊比較快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴 你抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 免了吧 我一個人也能下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦 這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勒利斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 克勒利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞勒涅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.17,0:08:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些擁有強大小宇宙的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間沒有被停止 逃過一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到距離城堡如此之近的地下 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這麼多倖存者…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭到刻鬥士的襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:09:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城裡的絕大多數人的時間都被奪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些死裡逃生的人們 便藏身此處
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艱難維生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你並非為了雅典娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是為了這些人而戰…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我很清楚雅典娜的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來 距離帕拉斯的城堡最近的我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理應去衝鋒陷陣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿命…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小馬座的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您身上聖衣的宿命嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.71,0:09:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些破事都是迷信啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 塞勒涅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給天馬座他們沏點茶 好好招待著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勒利斯你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.96,0:09:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倉庫 我去把上面的門關上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你剛才說的小馬座的宿命是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前略有耳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小馬座是被詛咒的聖衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身披小馬座聖衣者將被引向死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上那聖衣 就會死的意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說 小馬座聖鬥士以獲得強大的力量為代價
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.82,0:10:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定將在戰鬥中失去生命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知如此 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何還要穿上那聖衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.62,0:10:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為即使以命相賭 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想得到力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 你大概是不會理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明身上流淌著神之血 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻還叫嚷著「不需要神之血」的你 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不會理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勒利斯真正的目的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要不分對象地見人就咬嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這話是什麼意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候 只需要說聲謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接過來就好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞勒涅 也給我來一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.35,0:11:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勒利斯 你也該解釋一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我們帶到這裡來的理由了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.89,0:12:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座地下城與帕拉斯城是相通的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與帕拉斯城相通…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出生成長在這座城市 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座不知建成於何時的地下城
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像迷宮一般迂迴深入
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直延伸到帕拉斯的城堡附近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.51,0:12:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好極了 一口氣直搗帕拉斯的城堡吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.19,0:12:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒能阻止刻鬥士的進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能保護許多生命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我已經下定決心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:13:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不會讓這裡的任何人受到一絲一毫的傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 搞什麼啊 真讓我失望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本以為你是為了追求強大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才穿上那身聖衣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來只是個沒種的膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勒利斯很強的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.06,0:13:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為了保護大家 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得這樣 遍體鱗傷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.01,0:13:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為了我們拚命戰鬥 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個勇敢的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正 不管怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去把帕拉斯打得找不著北
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勒利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們好像被那些刻鬥士跟蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.35,0:14:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隕石召喚 惡魔之錘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士和苟延殘喘的人類們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你們藏在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給老子滾出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為我跑了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會立刻把他們趕走的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勒利斯 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你留在這裡保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.89,0:14:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴 你也留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 你的鋼鐵聖衣損傷太嚴重了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟過來也是累贅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是累贅？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.21,0:15:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊就交給他們吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我好好珍惜生命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.08,0:15:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我 克勒利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小宇宙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從地下來的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼 又是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原話奉還 你這軟骨頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.52,0:15:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我打！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到人類竟潛伏到了通往城堡的地下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能從這裡入侵城堡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 當然也能從城堡來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度的迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑我的耳朵 輕易就可探出正確的路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也不知道就跟了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈提從地下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爺從地上 一同夾擊 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是完美的作戰策略
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們無路可逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈提
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會讓你胡作非為的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那破爛聖衣還能幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:17:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然以小宇宙為盾牌彈開了短劍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別亂來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的短劍可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂來的是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿著破損的聖衣還想正面迎敵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.85,0:17:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對聖衣的那份心意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經傳遞給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.88,0:17:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被穿著受詛咒的聖衣的傢伙說教
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也沒有說服力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它沒有被詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.17,0:17:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聖衣想要保護生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小馬座聖衣當人陷入絕境 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鈞一髮時就會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是向弱者伸出援助之手的 十分體貼的聖衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,群星在失去生命之前 會綻放更強烈的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小馬座聖鬥士也是同樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就在發光後 徒然死去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勒利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.23,0:18:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡魔之錘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷電·赫拉克勒斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈提那小子 到底在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼獅熾焰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神聖龍捲風
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼摩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子可不管哈提那小子的死活了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你們全部轟飛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忒拜那混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把我們都轟飛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被捲進來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.26,0:19:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體給我撤！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.09,0:19:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被卷進去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.68,0:20:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勒利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去不太妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看未必
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本不想用這個的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這招實在太大又難控制 是禁斷的奧義
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你所說的強大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前問過我 為什麼會變強
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時的我 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有了應守護的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去需要保護的人時 確實可能強大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有應守護之人的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份強大無法估量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂糟糟一堆廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:20:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.91,0:21:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨大小行星（Gigantic Asteroid）！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轟鳴吧 我的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獵戶絕滅！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我軟弱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爺我軟弱嗎！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:21:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.72,0:22:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應守護的人 是你讓我察覺到了那份強大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.12,0:22:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.46,0:22:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.76,0:22:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小馬座的光輝引導的 是死亡的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.86,0:22:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互交織的紐帶不再迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在克勒利斯熾熱的靈魂
